Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
delete_metric_table_heading(25.10)          delete_metric_table_heading(25.10)

Name
       delete_metric_table_heading - Deletes a metric heading

Syntax
       delete_metric_table_heading

       [-help]

       [-format {html excel text}]

       [-id <heading_id>]

       Deletes a metric heading.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man delete_metric_table_heading

       -format {html excel text}
              Specifies configuration for the specified report_metric format.

              Data_type: enum, optional

       -id <heading_id>
              Specifies the id of the heading to be deleted.

              Data_type: string, optional

Related Information
              * report_metric

